{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idc3bf92ce-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87","identifier":"/us/usc/t38/s4110B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"4110B"},"text":"§ 4110B.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Coordination and nonduplication","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"In carrying out this chapter, the Secretary shall require that an appropriate administrative entity in each State enter into an agreement with the Secretary regarding the implementation of the Workforce Innovation and Opportunity Act that includes the descriptions described in sections 102(b)(2)(B)(ii) and 103(b)(3)(A) of the Workforce Innovation and Opportunity Act and a description of how the State board will carry out the activities described in section 101(d)(3)(F) of such Act.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idc3bf92cf-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87"},"text":"(Added ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/105/220/tIII/s322"},"text":"Pub. L. 105–220, title III, § 322","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1998-08-07"},"text":"Aug. 7, 1998","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/112/1087"},"text":"112 Stat. 1087","children":[],"tail":"; amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/109/233/tV/s503/13"},"text":"Pub. L. 109–233, title V, § 503(13)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2006-06-15"},"text":"June 15, 2006","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/120/417"},"text":"120 Stat. 417","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/113/128/tV/s512/gg/4"},"text":"Pub. L. 113–128, title V, § 512(gg)(4)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2014-07-22"},"text":"July 22, 2014","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/128/1719"},"text":"128 Stat. 1719","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idc3bf92d0-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idc3bf92d1-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"idc3bf92d2-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Workforce Innovation and Opportunity Act, referred to in text, is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/113/128"},"text":"Pub. L. 113–128","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2014-07-22"},"text":"July 22, 2014","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/128/1425"},"text":"128 Stat. 1425","children":[],"tail":", which enacted chapter 32 (§ 3101 et seq.) of Title 29, Labor, repealed chapter 30 (§ 2801 et seq.) of Title 29 and chapter 73 (§ 9201 et seq.) of Title 20, Education, and made amendments to numerous other sections and notes in the Code. Sections 101(d)(3)(F), 102(b)(2)(B)(ii), and 103(b)(3)(A) of the Act are classified to sections 3111(d)(3)(F), 3112(b)(2)(B)(ii), and 3113(b)(3)(A), respectively, of Title 29. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t29/s3101"},"text":"section 3101 of Title 29","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"idc3bf92d3-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2014—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/113/128"},"text":"Pub. L. 113–128","children":[],"tail":" substituted “enter into an agreement with the Secretary regarding the implementation of the Workforce Innovation and Opportunity Act that includes the descriptions described in sections 102(b)(2)(B)(ii) and 103(b)(3)(A) of the Workforce Innovation and Opportunity Act and a description of how the State board will carry out the activities described in section 101(d)(3)(F) of such Act” for “enter into an agreement with the Secretary regarding the implementation of the Workforce Investment Act of 1998 that includes the description and information described in paragraphs (8) and (14) of section 112(b) of the Workforce Investment Act of 1998 ("},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t29/s2822/b"},"text":"29 U.S.C. 2822(b)","children":[],"tail":")”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2006—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/109/233"},"text":"Pub. L. 109–233","children":[],"tail":" substituted “implementation of the Workforce Investment Act of 1998” for “implementation of this Act” and inserted “("},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t29/s2822/b"},"text":"29 U.S.C. 2822(b)","children":[],"tail":")” before period at end."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"idc3bf92d4-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDateOfAmendment","id":"idc3bf92d5-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Effective Date of 2014 Amendment","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Amendment by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/113/128"},"text":"Pub. L. 113–128","children":[],"tail":" effective on the first day of the first full program year after "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2014-07-22"},"text":"July 22, 2014","children":[],"tail":" ("},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2015-07-01"},"text":"July 1, 2015","children":[],"tail":"), see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/113/128/s506"},"text":"section 506 of Pub. L. 113–128","children":[],"tail":", set out as an Effective Date note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t29/s3101"},"text":"section 3101 of Title 29","children":[],"tail":", Labor."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
